1264
01:15:52,702 --> 01:15:53,815
Buddie.

1265
01:15:54,815 --> 01:15:55,993
Pappy.

1266
01:15:56,511 --> 01:15:57,558
Jack.

1267
01:15:58,111 --> 01:15:59,354
Pappy!

1268
01:16:04,639 --> 01:16:06,581
Buddie! Buddie!

1269
01:16:08,959 --> 01:16:10,104
Buddie!

1270
01:16:21,023 --> 01:16:22,485
