1299
01:18:26,687 --> 01:18:29,021
It all seems kind of brutaI and
primitive while it's a-boiling,

1300
01:18:29,086 --> 01:18:32,086
but, well, I was born here and I know.

1301
01:18:33,055 --> 01:18:35,226
I'm talking honest,
Mr. Hale.

1302
01:18:35,775 --> 01:18:37,335
You know, I...

1303
01:18:37,407 --> 01:18:40,189
I cried when they told me
Buddie was killed.

1304
01:18:40,447 --> 01:18:42,008
Why, I used to ride miles
out of my way

1305
01:18:42,079 --> 01:18:43,867
to fetch him
some stick candy.

1306
01:18:44,190 --> 01:18:46,078
