01:19:02,879 --> 01:19:04,537
Yes, I could.

1315
01:19:04,606 --> 01:19:08,501
But did you ever get up close to
Melissa and look into her eyes?

1316
01:19:08,575 --> 01:19:09,655
Well, you do that
sometime.

1317
01:19:09,727 --> 01:19:11,549
Then you tell me
what kind of a law

1318
01:19:11,615 --> 01:19:14,103
you can think of
