1319
01:19:14,687 --> 01:19:16,148
Tell me...
June!

1320
01:19:25,215 --> 01:19:27,703
He couldn't just die,
could he?

1321
01:19:28,702 --> 01:19:30,393
He had to be killed.

1322
01:19:31,103 --> 01:19:32,859
Killed by the Falin.

1323
01:19:32,927 --> 01:19:34,356
They did that.

1324
01:19:35,070 --> 01:19:36,826
He was my only brother.

1325
01:19:36,894 --> 01:19:38,553
And they killed him.

1326
01:19:39,583 --> 01:19:42,681
He ran down the hill with
me before I went away.

1327
01:19:43,006 --> 01:19:45,625
He stood up there
at the Lonesome Pine.

1328
01:19:46,271 --> 01:19:48,376
I never got to
see him again.

1329
01:19:49,663 --> 01:19:52,030
I'm never going to
see him again.

1330
01:19:53,759 --> 01:19:55,221
What are you doing here?

1331
01:19:55,295 --> 01:19:57,433
Why aren't you up there
with Dave and Daddy?

1332
01:19:58,335 --> 01:20:00,091
You loved Buddie,
didn't you?

1333
01:20:00,159 --> 01:20:01,981
You said you loved him.

1334
01:20:03,262 --> 01:20:04,986
He was gonna be an engineer.

1335
01:20:05,055 --> 01:20:06,745
Like you and Corsey.

1336
01:20:08,799 --> 01:20:11,548
When I tucked him in
at night, he said,

1337
01:20:12,766 --> 01:20:17,655
" A is for apple, and I'll bet
you I'll be as big as Mr. Hale. "

1338
01:20:18,782 --> 01:20:19,960
What are you doing here?

1339
01:20:20,031 --> 01:20:21,078
June.

1340
01:20:21,918 --> 01:20:23,642
You're down here
with the law!

1341
01:20:23,743 --> 01:20:25,466
The law's gonna help you!

1342
01:20:25,598 --> 01:20:27,987
The laws gonna show you
how it don't hurt.

1343
01:20:28,063 --> 01:20:29,972
When somebody you love...

1344
01:20:30,046 --> 01:20:31,061
When somebody you love...

1345
01:20:31,135 --> 01:20:32,083
Oh, June, darling,
don't cry.

1346
01:20:32,159 --> 01:20:34,745
You mustn't cry.
Listen to me, dear.

1347
01:20:34,815 --> 01:20:36,408
I love you, and...

1348
01:20:38,846 --> 01:20:40,123
You love me?

1349
01:20:41,118 --> 01:20:43,060
You said
you loved Buddie.

1350
01:20:43,742 --> 01:20:45,652
Why aren't you
with Buddie?

1351
01:20:45,727 --> 01:20:47,963
Why aren't you
where they need you?

1352
01:20:48,030 --> 01:20:49,852
You're here
with the law.

1353
01:20:49,919 --> 01:20:50,998
You don't love me!

1354
01:20:51,070 --> 01:20:52,980
Well, I do
with all of my heart.

1355
01:20:53,055 --> 01:20:56,732
You never said you love me before
and I was hungry to hear it.

1356
01:20:57,790 --> 01:20:59,579
You said
you love Buddie.

1357
01:20:59,647 --> 01:21:01,752
But you ain't
doing nothing about it!

1358
01:21:01,822 --> 01:21:04,343
You ain't fighting!
You ain't killing!

1359
01:21:04,414 --> 01:21:07,164
That's what's coming
to them! The Falins!

1360
01:21:10,143 --> 01:21:11,998
This is what you wanted
me to be, ain't it?

1361
01:21:12,063 --> 01:21:14,267
Pretty, nice words,
hollow words!

1362
01:21:14,718 --> 01:21:16,147
I don't want it!

1363
01:21:16,222 --> 01:21:18,459
I don't want you!
I don't want anything!

1364
01:21:18,527 --> 01:21:20,414
I don't want anything
but the Falins!

1365
01:21:46,975 --> 01:21:50,270
Our Father who art in
Heaven, hallowed be thy name.

1366
01:21:50,686 --> 01:21:53,785
Thy Kingdom come. Thy
will be done on earth

1367
01:21:53,855 --> 01:21:55,480
as it is in Heaven.

1368
01:21:55,550 --> 01:21:59,063
Give us this day our daily bread
and forgive us our trespasses

1369
01:21:59,134 --> 01:22:01,917
as we forgive those
who trespass against us.

1370
01:22:02,751 --> 01:22:06,941
Lead us not into temptation
but deliver us from eviI.

1371
01:22:07,551 --> 01:22:11,446
For thine is the power and
the glory forever and ever.

1372
01:22:12,351 --> 01:22:13,431
Amen.

1373
01:22:24,063 --> 01:22:30,205
<i>When it's twilight on the trail</i>

1374
01:22:31,903 --> 01:22:35,416
<i>And I rest once more</i>

1375
01:22:37,726 --> 01:22:40,792
<i>My ceiling is the sky</i>

1376
01:22:42,270 --> 01:22:43,830
<i>And the grass</i>

1377
01:22:45,183 --> 01:22:47,484
<i>On which I lie</i>

1378
01:22:48,094 --> 01:22:50,680
<i>Is my floor</i>

1379
01:22:53,727 --> 01:23:00,088
<i>When it's twilight on the trail</i>

1380
01:23:02,559 --> 01:23:06,137
<i>And my voice is still</i>

1381
01:23:09,470 --> 01:23:12,819
<i>Please plant
this heart of mine</i>

