who he was shooting at.

1461
01:28:50,366 --> 01:28:52,700
Buddie Tolliver
couldn't say that.

1462
01:28:53,854 --> 01:28:56,025
I don't like him and
I ain't gonna like him.

1463
01:28:56,094 --> 01:28:58,069
I get my hands
on that Dave Tolliver...

1464
01:29:02,430 --> 01:29:03,607
Who's that?

1465
01:29:03,678 --> 01:29:05,107
Dave Tolliver.

1466
01:29:12,542 --> 01:29:14,036
What are you here for?

1467
01:29:14,110 --> 01:29:15,484
I wanna talk to you.

1468
01:29:15,550 --> 01:29:17,460
And I ain't carry no gun.

1469
01:29:28,766 --> 01:29:30,108
Come on in.

1470
01:29:38,751 --> 01:29:42,711
